'''Immaculée Ilibagiza''' (wavutse 1972) mu [[Rwanda]] <ref name="BIO">http://www.architectsofpeace.org/architects-of-peace/immaculee-ilibagiza</ref> ni umunyarwandakazi wamamaye mu kwandika ibitabo.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Immaculée Ilibagiza yize ibijyanye n’ubuhanga mu bya elegitoroniki n’ubukanishi hanyuma ahabwa impamyabumenyi ya dogiteri na kaminuza ya Saint John (New York) <ref name="HH">http://www.hayhouse.com/left-to-tell-7?/fund</ref> .Ni umwanditsi akaba n'umuvugizi w'amahoro, kwizera n'imbabazi
<ref name="HMS">http://www.humanitysteam.fr/IMMACULEE-ILIBAGIZA_a295.html</ref>Igitabo cye cya mbere, ''Left to Tell: Discovering God Amidst the Rwandan Holocaust'' (2006) (yacyanditse mugifaransa  : Igitangaza [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|.]]  [[1994|_]] Aguma yihishe iminsi 91, hamwe n’abandi bagore barindwi, mu bwiherero buto, yihishe mu cyumba cyihishe mu kabati mu nzu y’umushumba w’umuhutu  Nzabahimana <ref name="TNYT">https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F05E0DA1F30F935A25757C0A9609C8B63&sec=&spon=&&scp=2&sq=immaculee&st=cse</ref> . Mu gihe cya jenoside, benshi mu bagize umuryango wa Immaculée Ilibagiza bishwe [[Interahamwe|n’interahamwe]] . : nyina, ise na barumuna be Damascene na Vianney. We na murumuna we Aimable ni bo barokotse bonyine. : Aimable yigaga muri [[Senegali]] kandi ntabwo yari azi ko genocide  ikomeje. Mu gitabo cye, Immaculée Ilibagiza asobanura uburyo imyizerere ye Gatolika yamuyoboye mu ngorane. Asangiye imbabazi n'impuhwe abicanyi bo mumuryango we.Agaragara kumurongo wa tereviziyo ya rubanda muri gahunda ya Wayne Dyer ariko nanone Ku ya 3 Ukuboza 2006 muri gahunda Iminota 60 (reba Ku ya 1 Nyakanga 2007 ) <ref name="CBS">http://www.cbsnews.com/news/rwandan-genocide-survivor-recalls-horror/</ref> .Immaculée Ilibagiza atanga ubuhamya ku isi yose kandi ahabwa igihembo cya Mahatma Gandhi kubera Ubwiyunge n'Amahoro mu 2007.

Kugira ngo ahunge jenoside, yimukiye [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika|muri Amerika]] mu 1994 maze aba umunyamerika ufite ubwenegihugu muri 2013 <ref name="HUFF">http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/12/18/happy-photos-2013_n_4427777.html?1387728258&</ref> .
Immaculate Ilibagiza yashakanye na Bryan Black, Umunyamerika ukorera [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|Umuryango w’abibumbye]] ku byaha by’intambara mu Rwanda. Bryan ni Umuyobozi wungirije ushinzwe umutekano ku cyicaro cya Loni <ref name="TNYT2">https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F05E0DA1F30F935A25757C0A9609C8B63&sec=&spon=&&scp=2&sq=immaculee&st=cse</ref> Akora nk'umufasha muri gahunda y’iterambere ry’umuryango w’abibumbye <ref name="TNYT2" /> i [[New York]] maze ashinga umusingi ( ''Immaculee's Health Mission'' ) wo gufasha abana b’imfubyi n’abazize intambara <ref name="AFRI">http://www.africultures.com/php/index.php?nav=personne&no=18895</ref> . Iki kigega cyakusanyije  arenga 200 000  y’impfubyi mu [[Rwanda]] <ref name="TNYT2" />

